::Killfest/Greven/Scyther/EndBringer/Demise::

Looks of surprize were written on every member's face as they saw a 
small femm walk out of the room, Killfest following her. This was not 
what they had expected, after being led by Killfest, who towered over 
this femm.

"This is my team," Killfest says, walking down the line to introduce 
them.

"EndBringer, specialized in causing carnage on the battle," Killfest 
says, EndBringer nodding.

"Demise, pain specialist."

Demise nodded his monstrous head, the beast-bot looking at KitKat.

"Greven, excellent fighter, excellent in battle."

Greven nods, moving his large head slowly.

"And Scyther, specialized in undercover missions, assassinations, 
whatever is needed."

Scyther, the only one in the hallway that didn't tower over KitKat, 
nods, looking at her with red optics.
